self\">6761-TW</a>)、創新服務 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:7828:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7828\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7828-TW</a>)、精測 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6510:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6510\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6510-TW</a>)、崇越電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3388:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3388\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3388-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>個股詳細解析：</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>長興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1717:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1717\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1717-TW</a>)：電子材料：包括乾膜光阻、玻纖布、銅箔。台積電 CoWoS 封裝材料。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>昇陽半 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8028:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8028\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8028-TW</a>)：再生晶圓龍頭。再生晶圓使用量 3 奈米 23-28 片提升至 2 奈米的約 27-35 片。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>中砂 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1560:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1560\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1